  <div class="container">

    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What is CMPLTR? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>CMPLTR, short for Completer, is a progress routine manager that notifies you when to do your task and rewards
        you for each consecutive day completed. After completing your task for the day, you enter it in the app, and it
        rewards you with visual and auditory positive feedback.</p>
      </div>

     <!--- <b><label for="title">Q: What is CMPLTR?</label></b>
