    </div>

    <hr class="divider">
    </hr>

    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What does the "Create Routine" button do? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>It allows you to create and customize a routine that you intend to follow. 
        You title it, set the total amount of days to complete, set the alarm, and optionally 
        establish the goals and goal rewards for the routine.</p>
      </div>

    
      <!-- <b><label for="title">Q: What does the "Create Routine" button do?</label></b>
