    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What does the "Current Routines" button do? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>It shows you all of your active routines that need to be completed. You can click on a specific routine to check your progress,
        as well as, logging your progress.</p>
      </div>

     <!-- <b><label for="title">Q: What does the "Current Routines" button do?</label></b>
