    </hr>

    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What does the "Previous Routines" button do? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>It is an archive of all previous routines that have been finished. You cannot edit them, but you can view them.</p>
      </div>

