    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What does the "See Community Feed" button do? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>It shows you the activity of other users of the app and their progress on their routines.</p>
      </div>

    <!--  <b><label for="title">Q: What does the "See Community Feed" button do?</label></b>
