    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What do the circles on Current and Previous Routine mean? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>The circles represent each day that is to be completed for the routine. After doing the task for the specified
        day, you press the circle and it lights up.</p>
      </div>

     <!-- <b><label for="title">Q: What do the circles on Current and Previous Routine mean?</label></b>
