    <div>
      <button class="collapsible">Q: What happens when you finish a routine? <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></button>
      <div class="content">
      <p>After confirming you are logging the last day, it will ask you to confirm what goals you have finished. Afterwards, your routine
        will be archived in the previous routines page, where you can view it at any time.</p>
      </div>

